& [CurrentAttentionJournalState] is the live journal state for attention and intention chain replay
  + [state_status] is active
  + [journal_root] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\events\journals
  + [journal_contract] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\AttentionJournal.sop
  + [current_journal_stream] is attention_journal_system_bootstrap_stream
  + [latest_event] is attention_event_2026_06_28_attention_journal_continuity_002
  + [previous_event] is attention_event_2026_06_28_attention_journal_system_001
  + [active_intention_chain] is intention_chain_attention_journal_system
  + [root_intention] is make a journal system to sort out attention and intention chains
  + [current_intention] is add time-space continuity and local-awareness pairing between journal and narrative
  + [active_continuity_frame] is continuity_attention_journal_system_001_to_continuity_002
  + [active_local_awareness_pair] is local_awareness_pair_attention_journal_and_narrative
  + [open_tail] is integrate AttentionJournal into future operating-loop, registry, and trailing-checksum updates when those files are safe to edit or explicitly selected
  + [journal_policy] is append-only factual attention events with temporal anchors, spatial anchors, and continuity edges before narrative interpretation when durable reconstruction matters
  + [promotion_boundary] is journal events may inform narrative, registry, periphery, turn bookmark, and operating loop records, but do not replace them
  + [outside] is hidden model attention, exact activation replay, old events not yet journaled, and runtime automation not built in this slice

  = must: read AttentionJournal.sop before treating journal events as durable structure
  = must: append new events rather than rewrite prior events
  = must: preserve time-space continuity separately from narrative meaning
  = must: keep open_tail visible until integration pointers are added to root contracts or future operating-loop records
  = should: use this state as the re-entry seed when a future turn asks what attention events happened
  - never: treat this state as complete history before 2026-06-28
